ActFirst Nations Goods and Services Tax Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 2 to the First Nations Goods and Services Tax Act (2009-2)
PrecisORDER AMENDING SCHEDULE 2 TO THE FIRST NATIONS GOODS AND SERVICES TAX ACT by adding the name of the Province of Saskatchewan and the name of four Indian Bands in Saskatchewan along with the name of the council of each Band and the description of each Band's reserves in Saskatchewan, where the Band's provincial-type tax may apply.
